##Synopsis
10/05/2024 _ Assessment 3 of Data Structures and Algorithms

##Introduction
This DSA system is designed to manage contacts efficiently using hash table with chaining to handle collisions. It provides functionalities such as adding, deleting, updating, searching, sorting, and filtering contacts based on various criteria.

